NK012(na)001:0: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i sgrub skor las rog phur
NK012(na)001:1: gyi gzhung pod phrin las rol pa'i bang mdzod ces
NK012(na)001:3: bla ma dang dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:4: rig pa'i nyi ma sgrib gnyis chu 'dzin las //
NK012(na)001:5: yongs grol mi 'gyur mchog bde'i phur bu ches //
NK012(na)001:6: srid zhi'i 'khor lor ris med rgyas 'debs pa //
NK012(na)001:7: bla ma mchog dang rdo rje gzhon nur 'dud //
NK012(na)001:8: de yang snga 'gyur bstan pa'i gsal byed gnas brtan
NK012(na)001:9: lo ts+aa ba chen po ngag dbang chos dpal rgya
NK012(na)001:10: mtsho'i zhal nas / rig mchog 'bum sde las byung rtsa dum rgyud //
NK012(na)001:11: 'khrugs bsdebs snying por dril ba pad+ma yi //
NK012(na)001:12: zhal lung bdud rtsi'i nying khu mkhar chen baza'i //
NK012(na)001:13: thugs mtshor bskyil las legs babs lang lab kyi //
NK012(na)001:14: las gzhung sna nam sgom khog bcas pa'i khrigs //
NK012(na)001:15: rog dang so yi snyan brgyud 'bab stegs las //
NK012(na)001:16: dngos grub bdud rtsi'i zil dngar char chen du //
NK012(na)001:17: 'bebs byed brjod bde'i yig chas 'dir mtshon bya //
NK012(na)001:18: zhes gsungs pa ltar brgyud gsum kun 'dus dpal o
NK012(na)001:19: rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam b+ha wa'i
NK012(na)001:20: thugs dam gyi lha mchog rtsod pa med pa rdo
NK012(na)001:22: de nyid sgrub pa'i chos skor la kha ba'i ljongs 'dir bka' babs kyi bye brag las /
NK012(na)001:27: mkhon lugs la sogs pa mang du yod cing /
NK012(na)001:28: phyis tshod na gangs can ljongs kyi /
NK012(na)001:37: 'o bran la sogs pa'i sngags kyi rig 'dzin phal
NK012(na)001:38: che ba rdo rje phur pa'i grub thob yin cing
NK012(na)001:39: / de las skabs su babs pa phur pa rog lugs zhes yongs su grags pa 'di ni /
NK012(na)001:40: o rgyan rdo rje 'chang gi zhal gsung phrin las
NK012(na)001:41: phur pa rol pa'i rgyud sde bsam gyis mi khyab
NK012(na)001:43: gzhung 'di'i khungs kyi rgyud sde chen po sum cu rtsa gnyis te /
NK012(na)001:48: snying po'i don gyi rgyud lnga rnams kyi dgongs bcud dang /
NK012(na)001:49: khyad par du gyur pa bid+yot+ta ma la'i rtsa ba'i
NK012(na)001:50: rgyud kyi mngon par rtogs pa tshang la ma nor
NK012(na)001:51: bar nyung ngur ston pa'i le'u zhig bsdus te logs
NK012(na)001:52: su phyung nas / spyir rje 'bangs phal che ba la gnang zhing /
NK012(na)001:53: khyad par du pad+ma'i thugs bcud kyi chos drug la
NK012(na)001:54: sogs pa'i lo ts+aa ba mdzad pa po gnubs kyi
NK012(na)001:55: dge slong chen po nam mkha'i snying po la gnang
NK012(na)001:56: ba dang / de bzhin du chos rgyal chen po dang /
NK012(na)001:59: shud bu dpal gyi seng ge /
NK012(na)001:60: dpal gyi mchod gnas la sogs la gnang ba dang /
NK012(na)001:61: snying po'i yang bcud rnams jo mo mkhar chen bza'
NK012(na)001:62: ye shes mtsho rgyal la gnang nas de dag las
NK012(na)001:63: rim par grub pa thob pa bar ma chad pa
NK012(na)001:64: las brgyud de gangs can na phur pa'i grub thob
NK012(na)001:65: chen po zhes yongs su grags pa lang lab byang
NK012(na)001:66: chub rdo rje la phyi nang gsang gsum gyi ring
NK012(na)001:67: brgyud dang nye brgyud kyi bka' babs shing /
NK012(na)001:68: de las bka' srol mang du gyes pa las 'di
NK012(na)001:69: ni lang lab kyi bka' babs bu bzhi'i nang tshan
NK012(na)001:70: sna nam shes rab tshul khrims nas rim par rgya
NK012(na)001:71: ston sangs rgyas / rgya thung shes rab rgyal mtshan /
NK012(na)001:74: dpal lha ri ba rnams la rim par brgyud cing /
NK012(na)001:75: de las rog gi gdung las byon pa'i grub thob
NK012(na)001:76: chen po shes rab bla ma zhes o rgyan chen
NK012(na)001:77: po 'i sprul par grags pa de nyid kyis gsan
NK012(na)001:78: te sna nam lugs gtso bor mdzad pa'i bka' srol
NK012(na)001:80: de las rim par rog bkra shis grags pa la sogs rog gi rig 'dzin rnams dang /
NK012(na)001:81: so dpal mgon rgyal mtshan sogs so yi rig 'dzin
NK012(na)001:82: rnams kyi thugs dam du gyur pa'i chos skor 'di
NK012(na)001:83: la snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi bstan pa rgya mtsho'i
NK012(na)001:84: mnga' bdag chos rgyal gter bdag gling pa'i gsan yig
NK012(na)001:86: mngon par rtogs pa dum bur phyung ba'i rgyud sho
NK012(na)001:87: lo ka drug cu pa zhes gsungs pa ni rog
NK012(na)001:88: shes rab bla ma'i thugs sras rnal 'byor gyi dbang
NK012(na)001:89: phyug dpal mi bskyod rdo rje'am snye mo jo sras
NK012(na)001:90: bsod nams dpal gyis mdzad pa'i phur t+ai ka nyi
NK012(na)001:91: ma'i 'od zer gyi rtsa ba de yin pas 'dir
NK012(na)001:93: t+ai ka ni logs su yod pas 'di'i skor du gtogs par shes dgos shing //
NK012(na)001:94: las byang lang lab kyis rtsa dum 'khrugs sdebs dang sna nam gyi sgom khog dang bcas pa dang /
NK012(na)001:95: stod las rin chen phreng ba 'gro ba smin byed ces bya ba dang /
NK012(na)001:96: smad las dug phur nag po'i las byang dang /
NK012(na)001:97: phur pa'i dkyil 'khor du dam bsre zhing dbang bskur
NK012(na)001:98: ba'i rim pa zhes pa 'di gter chen gsung na
NK012(na)001:99: rin chen phreng ba zhes pa de yin nam snyam
NK012(na)001:100: ste / lo chen rin po che nas dbang bsgrigs
NK012(na)001:101: kyi rtsa ba 'di yin pas de las gzhan du
NK012(na)001:102: med 'dra bas de ltar na dpe tshan bzhi yod
NK012(na)001:104: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i phrin las sna nam chen
NK012(na)001:105: pos mdzad pa'i sgom khog dang bcas pa bzhugs so
NK012(na)001:106: // smyos kyi btsun pa d+harma sh+r+ai rdo rje rgyal po'i dape'o //
NK012(na)001:108: // bla ma dang dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:109: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos kyang //
NK012(na)001:110: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK012(na)001:111: sprul sku rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK012(na)001:112: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:113: theg mchog snying po phur pa yi //
NK012(na)001:114: bskyed rim lag len mthar thug ni //
NK012(na)001:115: zhal nas brgyud pa'i rim pa 'di //
NK012(na)001:116: go sla'i ched du 'dir bsgrigs so //
NK012(na)001:117: 'di nyams su len pa'i dus su /
NK012(na)001:120: tshogs ci 'byor pa gtsang zhing legs par bshams shing /
NK012(na)001:121: bdag nyid kyis sems can thams cad kyis sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob 'dod dang ldan pas /
NK012(na)001:122: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad bla ma la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:123: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:126: brgyud pa thams cad kyi rtsa ba bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:127: dngos grub thams cad kyi rtsa ba yi dam gyi lha tshogs rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:128: byin rlabs thams cad kyi rtsa ba ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:129: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:130: rig 'dzin brda'i brgyud pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:131: gang zag snyan khungs kyi brgyud pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:132: d+ha na sam skri ta la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:133: o rgyan gyi slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:134: ma ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro mtsho rgyal la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:135: sras +aa tsar gsal le la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:136: jo bo lang lab byang chub rdo rje la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:137: sna nam shes rab tshul khrims la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:138: rgya ston sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:139: rgya thung shes rab rgyal mtshan la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:140: rgya ston kha ser ba la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:141: a jo sman chung la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:142: dpal lha ri ba la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:143: rog shes rab bla ma la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:144: rog bkra shis grags pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:145: zhig po rin chen sku mched gsum la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:146: dpal ldan thams cad mkhyen pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:147: drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK012(na)001:148: sangs rgyas chos dang tshogs kyi mchog rnams la //
NK012(na)001:149: byang chub bar du bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK012(na)001:150: bdag gi sbyin sogs bgyis pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK012(na)001:151: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK012(na)001:152: sems can thams cad bde ba dang ldan /
NK012(na)001:154: myur du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub rin po che thob par bya //
NK012(na)001:155: de'i ched du bdag gis theg pa chen po gsang
NK012(na)001:156: sngags kyi lam 'di nyams su blang snyam du sems
NK012(na)001:157: bskyed // swa b+h+aa was stong par sbyangs /
NK012(na)001:159: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:161: bdag nyid dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu zhal gsum
NK012(na)001:162: phyag drug pa stod ye shes kyi khro bo la
NK012(na)001:163: / smad phur pa mgar gyi sol mal nas bton
NK012(na)001:164: pa lta bur gsal ba'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil
NK012(na)001:165: 'khor gyi steng du h'u mthing nag /
NK012(na)001:166: de las h'u bcu phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi /
NK012(na)001:167: steng 'og gnyis dang bcur h'u re re bsam /
NK012(na)001:169: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK012(na)001:171: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u /
NK012(na)001:172: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:173: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h'u /
NK012(na)001:174: da ha da ha h'u phata //
NK012(na)001:175: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h'u /
NK012(na)001:176: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:177: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK012(na)001:179: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai ba h'u /
NK012(na)001:180: hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:181: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h'u /
NK012(na)001:183: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h'u /
NK012(na)001:185: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h'u /
NK012(na)001:187: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK012(na)001:188: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:189: khro bo de dag kyang stod ye shes kyi khro
NK012(na)001:190: bo la smad phur pa mgar gyi sol mal nas
NK012(na)001:191: bton pa lta bu zhal phyogs bcur gzigs pas bar
NK012(na)001:192: chad thams cad bsrung bar gyur /
NK012(na)001:194: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK012(na)001:195: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK012(na)001:196: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK012(na)001:197: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK012(na)001:198: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK012(na)001:199: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK012(na)001:200: de bas bka' las ma 'da' zhig /
NK012(na)001:201: gsang ba'i mtshams las ma 'da' zhig /
NK012(na)001:204: gri h+na p+aa ya gri h+na p+aa ya h'u /
NK012(na)001:205: +aa na ya hoh b+ha ga wan /
NK012(na)001:206: b+aid+ya r+aa dza s+t+wa ba rak+sha na h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:208: khro bo rnams las khro chung dpag tu med pa 'phros /
NK012(na)001:209: g.yas phyogs su 'khor bas bgegs dang log 'dren thams
NK012(na)001:210: cad gsang sngags kyi ming tsam yang mi grags pa'i
NK012(na)001:211: sa na phar la bskrad par gyur /
NK012(na)001:212: g.yon skor du 'khor bas khro chung gi gur du gyur te /
NK012(na)001:213: bar chad kyi bgegs kyis mi tshugs par bsrung bar gyur /
NK012(na)001:214: e ma nga ni rang byung ba'i //
NK012(na)001:215: dpal chen khro rgyal nyid kyi sku //
NK012(na)001:216: steng gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:217: h'u chen k+aa ra nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:218: h'u chen k+aa ras dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:219: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:220: shar gyi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:221: rnam par rgyal ba nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:222: rnam par rgyal bas dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:223: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:224: shar lho phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:225: dbyug pa sngon po nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:226: dbyug pa sngon pos dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:227: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:228: lho yi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:229: gshin rje gshed po nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:230: gshin rje gshed pos dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:231: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:232: lho nub phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:233: mi g.yo mgon po nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:234: mi g.yo mgon pos dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:235: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:236: nub kyi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:237: rta mchog rgyal po nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:238: rta mchog rgyal pos dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:239: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:240: nub byang phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:241: gzhan gyis mi thub nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:242: gzhan gyis mi thub dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:243: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:244: byang gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:245: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:246: bdud rtsi 'khyil bas dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:247: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:248: byang shar phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:249: khams gsum rnam rgyal nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:250: khams gsum rnam rgyal dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:251: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:252: 'og gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs byung na //
NK012(na)001:253: stobs chen rgyal po nyid kyis zlog /
NK012(na)001:254: stobs chen rgyal pos dgra dang bgegs bzlog la //
NK012(na)001:255: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:256: mtshams bcad nang 'di tshun chod du //
NK012(na)001:257: su yang 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK012(na)001:258: gal te bka' las 'das gyur na //
NK012(na)001:259: phur pa lcags kyu 'khrigs pa yis //
NK012(na)001:260: snying nas drangs shing brdung bar bya //
NK012(na)001:261: de bas bka' las ma 'da' zhig /
NK012(na)001:262: gsang ba'i mtshams las ma 'da' zhig /
NK012(na)001:264: gnod par byed pa'i 'byung po mi dang mi ma
NK012(na)001:265: yin pa bdud dang bar du gcod pa bgegs rigs
NK012(na)001:266: stong phrag brgyad cu'i rigs su gyur pa /
NK012(na)001:267: mi min mi ru bardzu ba /
NK012(na)001:268: lha min lha ru bardzu ba /
NK012(na)001:269: gsang sngags nyan pa la mi dbang zhing /
NK012(na)001:270: phyag rgya lta ba la mi dbang ba /
NK012(na)001:271: bdud dang bar du gcod pa thams cad bskal pa'i me ri me dpung 'bar ba la /
NK012(na)001:272: srog chags sbrang bu mi gnas pa'am /
NK012(na)001:273: mar khol ma la chu'i thig pa mi gnas pa'am /
NK012(na)001:274: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la mun pa'i rdul mi gnas pa bzhin du gzhan na phar la dengs shig /
NK012(na)001:276: rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po gangs la nyi ma shar ba 'dra ba /
NK012(na)001:278: g.yas pa rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK012(na)001:279: g.yon pa dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK012(na)001:280: rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK012(na)001:281: dar sna tshogs kyis na bza' byas pa /
NK012(na)001:282: de'i thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h'u dkar po /
NK012(na)001:284: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes pa lan gsum brjod pas /
NK012(na)001:285: dang pos phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad spyan drangs /
NK012(na)001:286: gnyis pas dkyil 'khor lha tshogs spyan drangs /
NK012(na)001:287: gsum pas rig 'dzin rnams spyan drangs te /
NK012(na)001:288: mdun gyi nam mkhar pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK012(na)001:289: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK012(na)001:290: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK012(na)001:291: thugs rje nyi gsal 'od bzhin snyoms mdzad lha //
NK012(na)001:292: 'dir gshegs bdag la dgongs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:293: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK012(na)001:294: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga'i gtso //
NK012(na)001:295: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol pa yi //
NK012(na)001:296: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:297: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK012(na)001:298: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK012(na)001:299: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya chen yongs bkod de //
NK012(na)001:300: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK012(na)001:301: kun tu bzang mo gsang ba'i b+ha ga la //
NK012(na)001:302: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rab 'byams ma lus kun //
NK012(na)001:303: 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pas /
NK012(na)001:304: gnyis med byang chub sems kyis mnyes gyur cig /
NK012(na)001:305: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK012(na)001:306: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK012(na)001:307: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK012(na)001:308: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud //
NK012(na)001:309: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK012(na)001:310: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK012(na)001:311: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i tshogs //
NK012(na)001:312: 'byung dang 'byung 'gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK012(na)001:313: gsang chen rab dgyes gzugs can bdag nyid ma'i //
NK012(na)001:314: mkha' dbyings klong yangs pad+mo 'khyil ba la //
NK012(na)001:315: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal zhing //
NK012(na)001:316: ma bcos spros bral byang chub snying po'i sku //
NK012(na)001:317: cir yang snang ba bde chen g.yung drung lha //
NK012(na)001:319: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum bcu //
NK012(na)001:320: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK012(na)001:321: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK012(na)001:322: rigs lnga dpal chen khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK012(na)001:323: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK012(na)001:324: ye shes sprul pa'i lha tshogs mang po dang //
NK012(na)001:325: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK012(na)001:326: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod ma //
NK012(na)001:327: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnal 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK012(na)001:328: dpang gyur thugs rje'i dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:329: thugs rje'i gdung gsob rdo rje rnal 'byor bdag /
NK012(na)001:330: 'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK012(na)001:331: bla med go 'phang thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK012(na)001:332: bstan pa rgya mtsho so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK012(na)001:333: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor sdom pa'i mchog /
NK012(na)001:334: 'da' dka' rdo rje dam tshig can gyi gnyer //
NK012(na)001:335: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK012(na)001:336: snga phyi nos shing gnyer du smras so 'tshal //
NK012(na)001:337: yun du mi gtong 'da' bar mi bgyid de //
NK012(na)001:338: don la gol zhing ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK012(na)001:339: gzod bya long yod snyam pa'i le lo yis //
NK012(na)001:340: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung ba dang //
NK012(na)001:341: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med dbang gyur te //
NK012(na)001:342: sgom la mi brtson bsnyen sgrub g.yel la sogs //
NK012(na)001:343: tshor dang ma tshor ma rig dbang gis ni //
NK012(na)001:344: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK012(na)001:345: rnal 'byor gang zhig dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK012(na)001:346: skad cig tsam yang 'phrad par mi bya zhes //
NK012(na)001:347: bka' las byung zhing de ltar ma rtogs te //
NK012(na)001:348: gsang sgo 'chol ba'i dbye bsal dka' ba dang //
NK012(na)001:349: mngon shes chung bas skyon can ma rtogs te //
NK012(na)001:350: nyams dang tshogs 'dres nyams pa bskang ba dang //
NK012(na)001:351: nyams dang snod min rnams la chos bshad dang //
NK012(na)001:352: nyams la mi 'dzem nyams pa'i skyon gyis gos //
NK012(na)001:353: nyams sgrib skyon gyis gos par gyur to 'tshal //
NK012(na)001:354: tshe 'di'i rkyen dang yun gyis sgrib pa rnams //
NK012(na)001:355: rab gnong 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK012(na)001:356: mkha' ltar khyab pa'i thugs rje che mnga' ba //
NK012(na)001:357: byams pa'i thugs kyis bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK012(na)001:358: brtse ba'i thugs kyis bdag la nyer dgongs te //
NK012(na)001:359: ye shes lha tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK012(na)001:360: gnyis med btang snyoms ngang du bzhugs nas kyang //
NK012(na)001:361: gnyis med don gyi tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK012(na)001:362: don dam gnyis med spros dang bral ba la //
NK012(na)001:363: rnam rtog gang yang dmigs par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK012(na)001:364: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi dbang gis na //
NK012(na)001:365: nongs par mchis na rab gnong bzod par gsol //
NK012(na)001:366: bzod par gsol lo tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK012(na)001:368: lus rdo rje sku'i dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags /
NK012(na)001:369: ngag rdo rje gsung gi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags /
NK012(na)001:370: yid rdo rje thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK012(na)001:371: ma tshor ba rgyab nas nyams pa mthol lo bshags /
NK012(na)001:372: tshor ba mdun nas nyams pa mthol lo bshags /
NK012(na)001:373: dang po khas len ches pa mthol lo bshags //
NK012(na)001:374: bar du nyams len chung ba mthol lo bshags //
NK012(na)001:375: tha ma spyod lam rtsing pa mthol lo bshags //
NK012(na)001:376: mdor na rnal 'byor pa bdag cag gi lus ngag
NK012(na)001:377: yid gsum gyi sgo nas sku gsung thugs rtsa ba
NK012(na)001:378: dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams shing zhig ral
NK012(na)001:379: du gyur pa thams cad gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems
NK012(na)001:380: kyis mthol zhing bshags pas byang zhing dag par gyur
NK012(na)001:381: cig / badz+ra sa t+wa sa ma ya /
NK012(na)001:383: badz+ra sa t+wa te no pa tish+tha /
NK012(na)001:386: a nu rak+to me b+ha ba /
NK012(na)001:390: tsit+tam sh+re yam ku ru h'u /
NK012(na)001:391: ha ha ha ha hoh b+ha ga w+aan sarba ta
NK012(na)001:392: th+aa ga ta badz+ra m+aa me muny+tsa badz+ri b+ha ba
NK012(na)001:393: ma h+aa sa ma ya sa t+wa +aah mdun gyi
NK012(na)001:394: nam mkha'i lha dang bla mar bcas pa rnams rang
NK012(na)001:395: gi lus ngag yid gsum la thim /
NK012(na)001:396: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib dag /
NK012(na)001:397: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK012(na)001:398: lus ngag yid gsum la chu la chu 'dres /
NK012(na)001:399: mar la mar 'dres pa ltar gnyis su med par 'dres /
NK012(na)001:400: sman byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK012(na)001:401: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:402: bdag rdo rje gzhon nur gsal ba'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du yi ge h'u /
NK012(na)001:403: de las ra ya kha gsum 'phros /
NK012(na)001:405: ra las ye shes kyi mes bsregs /
NK012(na)001:406: ya las ye shes kyi rlung gis gtor /
NK012(na)001:407: kha las ye shes kyi chus bkrus /
NK012(na)001:408: snod b+han+d+ha 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK012(na)001:410: las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su /
NK012(na)001:411: byang sems kyi steng du h'u /
NK012(na)001:412: shar dri chen gyi steng du /
NK012(na)001:413: lhor m+aam sa'i steng du s+w+aa /
NK012(na)001:414: nub rak+ta'i steng du +aah byang dri chu'i steng du h+aa /
NK012(na)001:415: pad+ma d+ha ra h+r+aih mthe bong la rta mgrin /
NK012(na)001:416: srin lag la yum mi pham ma /
NK012(na)001:417: de gnyis kyi bar du h+r+aihdamara po /
NK012(na)001:418: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK012(na)001:422: gnyis su med par sbyor ba byas /
NK012(na)001:423: sbyor mtshams nas byang chub kyi sems sku gsung thugs
NK012(na)001:424: kyi dngos grub dang bcas pa thams cad bdud rtsi'i
NK012(na)001:425: snod du babs / ye shes dang dam tshig gi bdud rtsi gnyis su med par 'dres //
NK012(na)001:426: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK012(na)001:427: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK012(na)001:428: zhes pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol /
NK012(na)001:429: d+harma a mri ta h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:430: mchod tshogs rnams la gtor bas nyes skyon dang dri ma'i tshogs thams cad dag /
NK012(na)001:431: bi shud+d+he a mri ta h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:432: mched rnams la gtor bas mkhon gcugs thams cad sbyangs /
NK012(na)001:433: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha la ha la h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:434: bdud rtsi'i zeg ma las khro chung dpag tu med
NK012(na)001:435: pa 'phros pas bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad gsang
NK012(na)001:436: sngags kyi ming tsam yang mi grags pa'i sa na
NK012(na)001:438: gtor ma byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK012(na)001:443: snga ma bzhin snod la phog /
NK012(na)001:445: de'i nang du ma s+aur+ya man+da la /
NK012(na)001:449: de gnyis kyi bar du bcud kyi dngos po de ser po /
NK012(na)001:453: gu h+ya hri sho sa ma ye h'u /
NK012(na)001:461: chos rdo rje dang ldan par gyur /
NK012(na)001:462: rak+ta byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK012(na)001:466: de'i nang du bcud kyi dngos po der dmar po gcig bsam /
NK012(na)001:467: +aahh+aum ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK012(na)001:468: ra zhu ba las rak+ta'i rgya mtsho dba' klong 'khrug
NK012(na)001:469: cing 'khyil bar zhun chen gyi kha chag can du
NK012(na)001:470: gyur / rnam lnga byin gyis brlab pa ni //
NK012(na)001:471: swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+he sarba d+harmahswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho &aham /
NK012(na)001:472: nyes skyon gyi dri ma'i tshogs thams cad dag /
NK012(na)001:480: snod kyi nang du lha mo mchod rdzas thogs pa mang por byin gyis brlabs pa la /
NK012(na)001:481: steng rdo rje rgya gram gyis kha bcad //
NK012(na)001:482: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK012(na)001:483: chos thams cad spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang du blo gnas par bya'o //
NK012(na)001:484: kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK012(na)001:485: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can la byams snying rje sgyu ma tsam /
NK012(na)001:487: de ltar snying rje bas don bya ba'i phyir //
NK012(na)001:488: nam mkha' stong pa'i go skabs su rang sems kyi
NK012(na)001:489: rnam pa yi ge h'u mthing ga rma bya'i sgro
NK012(na)001:490: lta bu zhig tu lhang nger gsal /
NK012(na)001:492: rdo rje khros pas zhe sdang gcod //
NK012(na)001:493: mtshon chen sngon po 'bar ba yis //
NK012(na)001:494: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK012(na)001:495: srog gi go ru shar ba dang //
NK012(na)001:496: snying gi dkyil du bsgom par bya //
NK012(na)001:497: stong pa nyid kyi rang sgra'o //
NK012(na)001:499: h'u las 'od zer grangs med pa 'phros /
NK012(na)001:501: rigs drug gi sems can thams cad la phog /
NK012(na)001:502: rang rang gi sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar byas /
NK012(na)001:507: h'u de las e gcig 'og gi phyogs su chad /
NK012(na)001:510: nam mkha' mthing nag gru gsum rgya dpag tu med pa /
NK012(na)001:512: h'u de las ya gcig nam mkha'i steng du chad /
NK012(na)001:515: rlung gi khams dkyil 'khor zla gam dud kha /
NK012(na)001:516: rngams su dpag tshad sa ya drug 'bum rgya nam mkha' dang mnyam pa /
NK012(na)001:518: h'u de las ra gcig rlung gi steng du chad /
NK012(na)001:521: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho zlum po dmar po /
NK012(na)001:522: rngams su dpag tshad 'bum phrag brgyad brgya rlung gi dkyil 'khor dang mnyam pa /
NK012(na)001:524: h'u de las ba gcig rak+ta'i rgya mtsho'i steng du chad /
NK012(na)001:527: mchog phran gyi sa gzhi gru bzhi ser po /
NK012(na)001:528: rngams su dpag tshad 'bum phrag nyis khri /
NK012(na)001:529: rgya rak+ta'i rgya mtsho dang mnyam pa /
NK012(na)001:531: h'u de las kem gcig mchog phran gyi sa gzhi'i steng du chad /
NK012(na)001:534: kem rus kyi ri rab sngo skya sog bu rting pa sprad pa lta bu /
NK012(na)001:535: dpag tshad brgyad khri rgya mtsho'i gting du nub pa /
NK012(na)001:536: dpag tshad brgyad khri rgya mtsho'i khar byung ba /
NK012(na)001:538: h'u de las ra gcig ri rab kyi steng du chad /
NK012(na)001:541: ye shes kyi me dpung dmar po ri rab kyi tshad du khyab pa /
NK012(na)001:543: h'u de las b+h+r+au gcig ye shes kyi me dpung gi nang du chad /
NK012(na)001:546: b+h+r+au bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la e b+h+r+au /
NK012(na)001:547: b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang phyi rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa /
NK012(na)001:548: nang thod pa skam rlon sna tshogs las grub pa /
NK012(na)001:549: dbus gru gsum mthing nag rdo rje 'greng bus spags pa /
NK012(na)001:550: phyi rol zla gam dmar po gsum gyis bskor ba /
NK012(na)001:551: mu khyud zlum po thod pa'i phreng ba can /
NK012(na)001:553: mu khyud zlum po rdo rje'i phreng ba can /
NK012(na)001:555: khyams gcig la sgo bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK012(na)001:556: 'byung po pho mos ya them ma them byas pa /
NK012(na)001:557: chu srin gyi thod pas rta babs byas pa /
NK012(na)001:558: lha chen po brgyad kyis ka ba byas pa /
NK012(na)001:559: klu chen po brgyad kyis gdung ma byas pa /
NK012(na)001:560: gza' chen po brgyad kyis phyam byas pa /
NK012(na)001:561: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis dral ma byas pa /
NK012(na)001:562: ru tra pho mo'i lpags pas thog phub pa /
NK012(na)001:563: nyi ma dang zla ba'i mthong dkar yod pa //
NK012(na)001:564: phyogs bzhir chos kyi 'khor lo bzhi dang /
NK012(na)001:566: zhing chung gi rgyal mtshan dang phyogs bzhir khrag gi zham chu 'babs pa /
NK012(na)001:567: gnam lcags kyi gzer thal ler btab pa /
NK012(na)001:568: tsit+ta'i tog chen po gcig tu gyur pa /
NK012(na)001:569: gru gsum mthing nag bco lngas brgyan pa /
NK012(na)001:570: phyi nas bltas na nang gsal ba /
NK012(na)001:571: nang nas bltas na phyi gsal ba /
NK012(na)001:576: w+aa ru na ti ra ba /
NK012(na)001:577: dbus gtso bo'i gdan steng du /
NK012(na)001:581: dregs pa khyo shug bsnol ba'i gdan /
NK012(na)001:582: dzahmh'u ba hoh 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad /
NK012(na)001:583: steng 'og gnyis dang bcur phyogs skyong bcu'i gdan /
NK012(na)001:584: sgo bzhi la'ang dgra bgegs kyi gdan /
NK012(na)001:585: dam can la'ang dgra bgegs kyi gdan /
NK012(na)001:587: rgyu'i yi ge h'u nag po de skar chen thang la babs pa ltar du /
NK012(na)001:588: gzhal yas khang gi gnam skar nas mar la babs te /
NK012(na)001:589: gtso bo'i gdan steng du 'od lam lam gsal ba la /
NK012(na)001:591: h'u las h'u grangs med pa 'phros /
NK012(na)001:593: rigs drug gi sems can thams cad la phog /
NK012(na)001:594: rang rang gi sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar byas /
NK012(na)001:600: rdo rje sngon po rtse dgu pa lte ba la yi ge h'u gis mtshan pa /
NK012(na)001:601: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:602: bdag nyid rdo rje gzhon nu tshon gang ba /
NK012(na)001:604: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:605: bdag nyid dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu sku che la yan lag rags pa /
NK012(na)001:606: sku mdog mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi pa /
NK012(na)001:607: zhal g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing /
NK012(na)001:608: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po na rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK012(na)001:609: bar pa na rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK012(na)001:610: g.yon gyi dang po na me dpung /
NK012(na)001:611: bar pa na kha t+w+aam ka /
NK012(na)001:612: tha ma gnyis ri rab kyi phur bu thugs kar 'dril ba /
NK012(na)001:613: zhabs bzhi'i mdun gnyis brkyang bskum du bzhugs pa /
NK012(na)001:614: rgyab gnyis gyad kyi dor stabs su bzhugs pa /
NK012(na)001:615: spyan dgu sdang mig dmar po bgrad pa /
NK012(na)001:616: ral pa kham pa gyen du 'khyil ba /
NK012(na)001:617: dbu la rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kyis brgyan pa /
NK012(na)001:618: glang po che'i ko rlon dang /
NK012(na)001:619: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi'i na bza' gsol ba /
NK012(na)001:620: stag gi lpags pa'i sham thabs byas pa /
NK012(na)001:621: thod skam gyis dbu brgyan pa /
NK012(na)001:622: thod rlon gyis dpung pa brgyan pa /
NK012(na)001:623: thod pa ra ri nyi shu rtsa lngas se ral kha byas pa /
NK012(na)001:624: sbrul rgyal rigs dkar khras dbu thod dang snyan cha byas pa /
NK012(na)001:625: bram ze ser khras mgur chu dang dpung rgyan byas pa /
NK012(na)001:626: rje'u rigs ser khras se ral kha byas pa /
NK012(na)001:627: dmangs rigs ljang khus sku rags byas pa /
NK012(na)001:628: gdol pa nag pos phyag gdub dang zhabs gdub byas pa /
NK012(na)001:632: smin mtshams khro gnyer rab tu bsdus pa /
NK012(na)001:635: zhal nas me stag gi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba /
NK012(na)001:636: h'u dang phata kyi sgra sgrogs pa /
NK012(na)001:637: lus thams cad khro chung gis gtams pa /
NK012(na)001:638: rdo rje'i gshog pa phyogs bcur brgyangs pa /
NK012(na)001:639: bskal pa'i me ri me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs par gyur /
NK012(na)001:640: de'i thugs kar tsit+ta smug po gur phub pa 'dra ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK012(na)001:641: snying tshil dkar dmar gdan nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK012(na)001:642: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba /
NK012(na)001:643: phyi rol ci 'dra ba la rgyan dang cha lugs spangs pa /
NK012(na)001:644: de'i sgo srog pa rtsar rta mgrin yab yum gyis bsrung ba /
NK012(na)001:645: de'i thugs kar tsit+ta smug po gur phub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK012(na)001:646: snying tshil dkar dmar gdan zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK012(na)001:647: steng du rdo rje 'greng pa rwa phyed zla ba'i
NK012(na)001:649: rwa phyed zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du phyung
NK012(na)001:650: ba'i lte ba la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK012(na)001:651: du yi ge h'u mthing nag spus bris pa tsam
NK012(na)001:652: / de'i mtha' ma nyi chung zla chung spel ma'i steng du /
NK012(na)001:653: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana ba h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:654: sngags 'di 'od ljang dmar du lam lam gsal ba la /
NK012(na)001:655: spyi bo las 'khor lo dkar po gyis mtshan pa /
NK012(na)001:656: mgrin par +aahls pad+ma dmar po +aahs mtshan pa /
NK012(na)001:657: snying gar h'u las rdo rje sngon po h'u gis mtshan pa /
NK012(na)001:658: thugs ka'i h'u las h'u gcig g.yon phyogs su chad /
NK012(na)001:659: d+aip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:660: yum 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma sku mdog mthing skya /
NK012(na)001:663: g.yon pas dung dmar gtso bo la stob pa /
NK012(na)001:664: rgyan chas yab dang mthun pa la gzig gi lpags pa'i sham thabs byas pa /
NK012(na)001:665: yab kyi gsang gnas su h'u las rdo rje sngon
NK012(na)001:666: po rtse dgu pa'i lte ba la yi ge h'u
NK012(na)001:667: gis mtshan pa / yum gyi gsang gnas su a
NK012(na)001:668: las pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma bzhi pa'i ze'u 'brur
NK012(na)001:669: gis mtshan pa / as mtshan pa / rdo rje dang pad+ma mnyam par sbyor zhing //
NK012(na)001:670: mkha' gsang bde ba rgyun mi chad pa'o //
NK012(na)001:672: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK012(na)001:673: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK012(na)001:674: phung po rdo rjer gtam byas nas //
NK012(na)001:675: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK012(na)001:676: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK012(na)001:677: srid pa rdo rjer grub mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:678: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK012(na)001:679: ye shes khro bo grub par mdzod //
NK012(na)001:680: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas phyogs skyong ba bcu'i gdan gyi steng du h'u bcu brjod /
NK012(na)001:682: h'u las h'u grangs med pa 'phros /

NK012(na)001:843: yum yang 'od du zhu nas phur pa la thim

NK012(na)001:973: gzhal yas sgo ma'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //

NK012(na)001:981: lnga'i mchod pa sngar bshams nas byin gyis brlabs pa

NK012(na)001:1061: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rin chen mang
NK012(na)001:1063: gzugs mdzes dam pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:1065: 'jigs pa thams cad dang bral ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:1066: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta a wa lo ki te sam b+ha ra sam b+ha ra h'u /
NK012(na)001:1067: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga dang ldan pa /
NK012(na)001:1068: mi zad pa'i gter chen po dang ldan par byin gyis brlabs pa 'di nyid yul phyogs dang /
NK012(na)001:1069: sa phyogs 'di na gnas pa'i gnas po gzhi bdag byang chub sems dpa' lha'i rigs su gyur pa /
NK012(na)001:1071: sa bdag sa srin gyi rigs su gyur pa /
NK012(na)001:1072: rgyal po'i rigs su gyur pa /
NK012(na)001:1073: bsen mo'i rigs su gyur pa /
NK012(na)001:1074: btsan gyi rigs su gyur pa /
NK012(na)001:1075: mdor na gzhi'i bdag po thams cad la mchod pa 'bul lo //
NK012(na)001:1076: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK012(na)001:1077: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa la sdod na ru ma nga /
NK012(na)001:1079: gzhi mgron sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu bsgrub pa la /
NK012(na)001:1080: chos dang mthun pa'i grogs dan mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:1081: dkar gtor yod na byin rlabs 'dra /
NK012(na)001:1082: klu chen po brgyad kyis gtsos byas pa'i /
NK012(na)001:1087: gdol pa'i rigs thams cad la 'bul lo //
NK012(na)001:1088: klu dang sa bdag gi tshogs thams cad zhe sdang
NK012(na)001:1089: dang gdug rtsub kyi bsam pa nye bar zhi nas
NK012(na)001:1090: phan pa byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur
NK012(na)001:1092: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK012(na)001:1094: rang byung gdod nas dag pa ste //
NK012(na)001:1095: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK012(na)001:1096: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK012(na)001:1097: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas /
NK012(na)001:1098: rgyud drug sems can thams cad kyi //
NK012(na)001:1099: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK012(na)001:1100: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK012(na)001:1101: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'dir //
NK012(na)001:1102: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK012(na)001:1103: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK012(na)001:1104: bla med 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK012(na)001:1105: tshangs pa 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK012(na)001:1106: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1107: bdud rtsi mtheb srin gyi nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor gyis nam mkha' la gtor la /
NK012(na)001:1108: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' //
NK012(na)001:1109: rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams la phul bas mnyes par gyur cig /
NK012(na)001:1110: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la 'bul ba ni /
NK012(na)001:1112: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK012(na)001:1113: bcom ldan rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum la //
NK012(na)001:1114: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1115: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1116: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1117: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK012(na)001:1118: 'jigs byed khro bo pha bcu ma bcu la //
NK012(na)001:1119: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1120: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1121: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1122: khro rgyal yab yum thugs las sprul pa'i sras //
NK012(na)001:1123: za byed gsod byed khra thabs nyi shu la //
NK012(na)001:1124: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1125: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1126: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK012(na)001:1127: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa yi //
NK012(na)001:1128: thugs rje sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la yar //
NK012(na)001:1129: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1130: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1131: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1132: dzahmh'u ba hohye shes sgo ma bzhi //
NK012(na)001:1133: gzhal yas sgo ma'i tshogs su gyur pa la //
NK012(na)001:1134: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1135: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1136: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1137: bdag nyid chen po shwa na mu kha dang //
NK012(na)001:1138: sa bdag bswe mo'i tshogs su gyur pa la //
NK012(na)001:1139: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1140: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1141: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1142: ging chen bco brgyad ging phran 'bum la sogs //
NK012(na)001:1143: lha yi dge bsnyen tshogs su gyur pa la //
NK012(na)001:1144: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1145: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1146: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1147: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams mnyes par gyur //
NK012(na)001:1148: 'dus pa mdo'i lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1149: sgyu 'phrul rgyan gyi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1150: 'jam dpal sku'i lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1151: pad+ma gsung gi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1152: yang dag thugs kyi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1153: bdud rtsi sman gyi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1154: phur pa phrin las kyi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1155: ma mo rbod gtong gi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1156: rig 'dzin slob dpon gyi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1157: dmod pa drag sngags kyi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1158: 'jig rten mchod bstod kyi lha tshogs kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1159: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi skyes bu ging
NK012(na)001:1160: chen bco brgyad skyes bu lang+ka grub pa ye shes
NK012(na)001:1161: kyi ma mo bdun sring mo bzhi 'bar ma myos
NK012(na)001:1162: byed brgyad pho nya drug cu rtsa bzhi dbang phyug
NK012(na)001:1163: nyi shu rtsa brgyad bod khams skyong ba'i brtan ma
NK012(na)001:1164: bcu gnyis bla ma brgyud kyi yang snang pa'i srung
NK012(na)001:1165: ma dben gnas gnyan gyi srung ma chos 'khor skyong
NK012(na)001:1166: ba'i srung ma pha mes brgyud kyi srung ma rnal
NK012(na)001:1167: 'byor bdag gi srung ma dpal ldan mgon po nag
NK012(na)001:1168: po ma gcig lha mo nag mo bka' sdod legs
NK012(na)001:1169: ldan nag po srin mo g.yag mgo bdun pa phyag
NK012(na)001:1170: brnyan rgya gar nag po sprul pa lcags spyang sngon
NK012(na)001:1171: mo gsod byed bshan pa dmar ba shan pa 'bum
NK012(na)001:1175: bla ma gong ma rnams kyis bka' dang dam la
NK012(na)001:1176: btags pa'i srung ma ma lus shing lus pa med
NK012(na)001:1177: pa thams cad kyi zhal du sarba pany+tsa a mri
NK012(na)001:1179: dam tshig dbang dang shes rgyud gab sbas pa'i //
NK012(na)001:1180: nges pa'i lung ston rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK012(na)001:1181: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1182: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1183: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1184: tshe rabs sngon nas las kyi 'phro mthun pa'i //
NK012(na)001:1185: dam tshig zungs kyis 'brel ba'i mched lcam la //
NK012(na)001:1186: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1187: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1188: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1189: 'das dang ma byon da ltar bzhugs pa yi //
NK012(na)001:1190: lus sems bskyed pa'i drin can pha ma la //
NK012(na)001:1191: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1192: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1193: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1194: dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK012(na)001:1195: lta ba 'phangs dmas chos nyid don ma rtogs //
NK012(na)001:1196: sgom pa yun thung yi dam lha ma gsal //
NK012(na)001:1197: 'bad rtsol chung bas slob dpon sku ma mnyes //
NK012(na)001:1198: brtse gdung chung bas mched lcam thugs dang 'gal //
NK012(na)001:1199: bkram pa'i lha tshogs rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK012(na)001:1200: lha tshogs rnams kyis skyes dang skyes lan gyi tshul du /
NK012(na)001:1201: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bdud rtsi'i snod du phab la /
NK012(na)001:1203: mu tig dkar po dri med dang //
NK012(na)001:1204: tsan+dana dmar po rma med dang //
NK012(na)001:1205: bswe phor dmar pho srub med gsum //
NK012(na)001:1206: bdud rtsi 'byung ba'i rgyu ni byang chub sems //
NK012(na)001:1207: bdud rtsi sgrub pa'i snod ni ka p+aa la //
NK012(na)001:1208: bdud rtsi'i nyid ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang //
NK012(na)001:1209: bdud rtsi'i las ni rnam rtog sbyong //
NK012(na)001:1210: bdud rtsi'i don ni skye shi med //
NK012(na)001:1211: rgyal ba mchod nas dngos grub blang ba ni //
NK012(na)001:1212: g.yon pa'i dam tshig rdo rje thal mo las //
NK012(na)001:1213: mthe bong dang ni srin lag rtse sbyar nas //
NK012(na)001:1214: bris pa bzhin du zla dkyil 'bru bkod de //
NK012(na)001:1215: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje thal mo la //
NK012(na)001:1216: rdo rje can gyis +aahmh'u sgom ste //
NK012(na)001:1217: bdud rtsi'i lnga yi sbyor ba yis //
NK012(na)001:1218: zos na bla med byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK012(na)001:1219: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK012(na)001:1221: yig 'bru gnas gsum du thim pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob /
NK012(na)001:1222: bdud rtsi gtor ma la sbreng ngo //
NK012(na)001:1224: sngar byin gyis brlabs pa'i rak+ta de khyad par can du byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK012(na)001:1225: rak+ta'i snod du dgra bgegs kyi ming bris la /
NK012(na)001:1227: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dgra bgegs 'byung po
NK012(na)001:1228: ha sa ya ra na ha sa ya ra na
NK012(na)001:1229: h+r+aihdan+da h'u phata / badz+ra +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1230: sh+r+ai g+h+ram +aa na ya sh+r+ai g+h+ram +aa na ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1231: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1232: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata //
NK012(na)001:1233: b+hin+d+ha ya b+hin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1234: ces brjod pas khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad phur pa'i rtse mo la hril hril 'dug par /
NK012(na)001:1235: de nyid khrag gi grod pa gcig tu gyur /
NK012(na)001:1236: de la phur pa btab pas stong gsum khrag gis gang bar gyur /
NK012(na)001:1237: bsgo ba'i bka' nyan pa'i don du /
NK012(na)001:1238: rak+ta dang po'i mchod pa ni /
NK012(na)001:1240: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK012(na)001:1241: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK012(na)001:1242: zungs shig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK012(na)001:1243: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK012(na)001:1244: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK012(na)001:1245: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK012(na)001:1246: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK012(na)001:1247: bsgo ba'i bka' la nyan par gyis //
NK012(na)001:1248: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1249: zhes phul bas sum gcig gsol /
NK012(na)001:1250: dgra bgegs bsgral zhing dam can gnad la dbab phyir rak+ta gnyis pa ni /
NK012(na)001:1251: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK012(na)001:1252: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1253: sngon chad ji bzhin dam bcas pa'i //
NK012(na)001:1254: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK012(na)001:1255: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ra kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1257: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul 'phrog pa'i phyir rak+ta gsum pa ni /
NK012(na)001:1258: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK012(na)001:1260: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK012(na)001:1261: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par byos //
NK012(na)001:1262: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ra kh+aa hi /
NK012(na)001:1263: rak+ta ma lus pa dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyis gsol /
NK012(na)001:1266: yab yum gyi rdo rje pad+ma byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK012(na)001:1267: mkha' gsang sbyor ba byas pa'i sbyor mtshams su dgra
NK012(na)001:1268: bgegs kyi lus rdul phran du bsam la /
NK012(na)001:1270: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK012(na)001:1271: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK012(na)001:1272: rdo rje me dbal snying bsregs nas //
NK012(na)001:1273: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK012(na)001:1274: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK012(na)001:1275: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NK012(na)001:1276: lha yang rung ste brlag par gyur //
NK012(na)001:1277: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u ba hoh dgra bgegs 'byung po shig m+aa ra ya /
NK012(na)001:1279: sh+r+ai g+h+ram ka ra ya ma ra se na pra mar+d+ha na ye /
NK012(na)001:1282: yum gyi sbyor mtshams su dgra bgegs kyi lus rdul phran du gyur /
NK012(na)001:1283: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK012(na)001:1284: sgrub pa po bdag cag la mchog thun mong gi
NK012(na)001:1285: dngos grub stsal du gsol zhig ces gsol ba gdab
NK012(na)001:1286: pa ni / srid pa'i phur bu sgrub pa dang //
NK012(na)001:1287: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK012(na)001:1288: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1289: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK012(na)001:1290: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK012(na)001:1291: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK012(na)001:1292: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1293: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1294: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1295: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1296: sa bdag bswe mo'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1297: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1298: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1299: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)001:1301: bdag cag rig 'dzin sgrub pa pos //
NK012(na)001:1302: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK012(na)001:1303: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung gsob pa'i //
NK012(na)001:1304: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK012(na)001:1305: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK012(na)001:1306: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK012(na)001:1308: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK012(na)001:1309: yud tsam gcig la 'dir khug la //
NK012(na)001:1310: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK012(na)001:1311: lus ngag rdul du bshig nas kyang //
NK012(na)001:1312: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK012(na)001:1313: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK012(na)001:1314: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK012(na)001:1315: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK012(na)001:1316: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK012(na)001:1317: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK012(na)001:1318: nga yi bka' las ma 'da' zhig /
NK012(na)001:1319: sgrub pa po bdag gi mchog thun mong gi dngos
NK012(na)001:1320: grub la bar du gcod pa thams cad thul cig
NK012(na)001:1322: bsnyen pa 'bul ba la bzla lugs gsum las /
NK012(na)001:1323: mgal me klad la bskor ba'i tshul du bzla ba ni /
NK012(na)001:1324: bdag 'dug sa b+han+d+ha 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK012(na)001:1325: bdag rdo rje gzhon nu zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK012(na)001:1326: zhabs bzhi yum dang bcas pa /
NK012(na)001:1327: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK012(na)001:1328: de'i thugs kar tsit+ta smug po gur phub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK012(na)001:1329: snying tshil dkar dmar nyi zla'i steng du ye shes
NK012(na)001:1330: sems dpa' de'i thugs kar tsit+ta smug po gur phub
NK012(na)001:1332: snying tshil dkar dmar gdan zla ba'i steng du /
NK012(na)001:1333: rdo rje 'greng bu rwa phyed zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la nub pa /
NK012(na)001:1334: rwa phyed zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyii steng du byung
NK012(na)001:1335: ba'i lte ba'i nang gi dal du h'u mthing ga
NK012(na)001:1339: zla chung spel ma'i steng du /
NK012(na)001:1340: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana ba h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1342: mdun du sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la ya /
NK012(na)001:1343: stod zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK012(na)001:1344: smad phur pa mgar gyi sol mal nas bton pa lta bu /
NK012(na)001:1345: zhal nang du gzigs pa'i thugs kar snying tshil dkar
NK012(na)001:1346: dmar gdan zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h'u
NK012(na)001:1349: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK012(na)001:1350: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK012(na)001:1351: phung po rdo rjer gtam byas nas //
NK012(na)001:1352: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer sgom //
NK012(na)001:1353: bdag khro bo'i go tshogs dang bcas pas sngags bzlas pas /
NK012(na)001:1354: thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer yig 'bru'i tshul du byung nas mtha' bskor gyi 'bru brgyud nas /
NK012(na)001:1355: rdo rje'i rtse nas ye shes sems dpa'i sna bug g.yas pa nas /
NK012(na)001:1357: bdag gi sna bug g.yas nas /
NK012(na)001:1358: sras mchog gi sna bug g.yon pa nas zhugs /
NK012(na)001:1359: mnyes mchod phul slar byung nas //
NK012(na)001:1360: sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad dag par bsam zhing bzlas pa bya'o //
NK012(na)001:1361: mgar gyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba'i tshul du bzla ba ni /
NK012(na)001:1362: bdag khro bo'i go tshogs dang bcas pas sngags bzlas pas /
NK012(na)001:1363: sngags las 'od zer me stag gi tshul du 'phros pas /
NK012(na)001:1364: dgra bgegs thams cad bya sgro me la bsregs pa ltar tshig par bsam la bazla'o //
NK012(na)001:1365: bung ba tshang zhig pa'i tshul du bzla ba ni /
NK012(na)001:1366: bdag khro bo'i go tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad
NK012(na)001:1367: kyis sngags bzlas pas lha tshogs thams cad kyang di
NK012(na)001:1369: chos nyid mi rtog pa'i ngang nas bzla /
NK012(na)001:1370: 'phro gcod pa'i dus su bstod pa ni /
NK012(na)001:1371: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK012(na)001:1372: srid pa rdo rje 'grub mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:1373: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK012(na)001:1374: ye shes khro bo grub par mdzod //
NK012(na)001:1376: gzhal yas khang gi nam mkhar sgra rang sgrar grags te /
NK012(na)001:1377: lha tshogs rnams la bstod par bsam /
NK012(na)001:1379: d+harma d+h+aa tu lhun gyis grub pa'i dbyings //
NK012(na)001:1380: bsod nams ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK012(na)001:1381: rgyal ba'i sprul sku rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK012(na)001:1382: pho nya las kyi tshogs la 'di skad bstod //
NK012(na)001:1383: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK012(na)001:1384: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK012(na)001:1385: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing nag po'i zhal //
NK012(na)001:1386: zhal g.yas dkar la bzhad par bstan pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1387: skye med chos kyi sku dang rab ldan te //
NK012(na)001:1388: khams gsum 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos rtags //
NK012(na)001:1389: zhal g.yon dmar la gdangs par bstan pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1390: thugs rje sprul pa'i sku dang rab ldan te //
NK012(na)001:1391: thugs rje sprul skus sems can don mdzad rtags //
NK012(na)001:1392: zhal dbus mthing la rngams par bstan pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1393: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang rab ldan te //
NK012(na)001:1394: chos dbyings rtogs nas dbyings las ma g.yos rtags //
NK012(na)001:1395: dbu gsum sku gsum rdzogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK012(na)001:1396: ral pa kham nag srid gsum gyen du bardzesa //
NK012(na)001:1397: smin mtshams khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK012(na)001:1398: spyan dgu nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor sdang mig gzigs //
NK012(na)001:1399: snyan gyi gsang bar dbyangs thos rig pas 'jug /
NK012(na)001:1400: shangs nas h'u 'byin zhal nas phata sgrogs shing //
NK012(na)001:1401: rno dbal mche gtsigs skye 'chi rtsad nas gcod //
NK012(na)001:1402: zhal gyi khro gnyer rdzogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK012(na)001:1403: phyag drug de ni g.yas kyi dang po na //
NK012(na)001:1404: rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams par bstan pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1405: sa dgu 'joms shing ye shes rdo rje ste //
NK012(na)001:1406: theg pa rim pa dgu yi spyi dbang yin //
NK012(na)001:1407: a ti yo ga lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1408: bar pa rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1409: 'khor bar 'khor ba'i dug lnga rtsad nas gcod //
NK012(na)001:1410: sku lnga ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1411: g.yon gyi dang po me dpung bsnams pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1412: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho gting nas skem //
NK012(na)001:1413: bag chags bud shing ma lus sreg pa'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1414: bar pa kha t+w+aam rtse gsum bsnams pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1415: brtson 'grus drag pos dug lnga rtsad bcad nas //
NK012(na)001:1416: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1417: tha ma thabs dang shes rab gnyis med kyi //
NK012(na)001:1418: byang chub sems kyi phur pa 'dril ba 'dis //
NK012(na)001:1419: khams gsum gdar gcod srid gsum zil gyis gnon //
NK012(na)001:1420: stong gsum dbang sdud dgra bgegs thal bar rlog /
NK012(na)001:1421: phyag drug phyag mtshan rdzogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK012(na)001:1422: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK012(na)001:1423: nyi zla pad+ma lha chen gdan steng du //
NK012(na)001:1424: zhabs gnyis thabs dang shes rab brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK012(na)001:1425: zhabs gnyis gyad kyi dor stabs gdug pa 'dul //
NK012(na)001:1426: zhabs kyi bzhugs thabs rdzogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK012(na)001:1427: sku stod glang chen klo rlon zhing lpags gsol //
NK012(na)001:1428: sku smad stag lpags sbrul gyi chun pos brgyan //
NK012(na)001:1429: thod phreng tshar gsum sku yi rgyan du mdzad //
NK012(na)001:1430: ba su thal chen khrag dang zhag gis mtshan //
NK012(na)001:1431: ru dra che chung sku rags mdzad pa 'di //
NK012(na)001:1432: 'khor ba ma spangs dbyings nas lhun grub rtags //
NK012(na)001:1433: sku yi rgyan rnams rdzogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK012(na)001:1434: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK012(na)001:1435: yab yum gnyis su med par bstan pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1436: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1437: yab kyi thugs kar ut+pala bsnams pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1438: 'gro ba'i don la thugs dam rgyud bskul rtags //
NK012(na)001:1439: yab yum gnyis su med la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK012(na)001:1440: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK012(na)001:1441: h'u mdzad la sogs khro bcus bskor ba ni //
NK012(na)001:1442: srid pa gsum na 'gran zla bral ba'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1443: sgra 'byin la sogs yum bcus bskor ba ni //
NK012(na)001:1444: dgyes pa chen pos mchod pa 'bul ba'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1445: khra thabs nyi shu'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK012(na)001:1446: zhing bcu bsgral nas 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1447: dpal chen 'khor tshogs bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK012(na)001:1448: snying rje'i stobs kyis sprul pa'i skur ston cing //
NK012(na)001:1449: drag po'i khro gzugs rngams pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK012(na)001:1450: 'jigs pa'i sprul bcings sangs rgyas dbu rgyan thod //
NK012(na)001:1451: sangs rgyas lnga yi 'bras bu k+ai la ya //
NK012(na)001:1452: 'jigs pa'i phyag mtshan 'debs pa'i tshul ston cing //
NK012(na)001:1453: sgrol ba'i stabs kyis gru gsum gdan la bzhugs //
NK012(na)001:1454: yang sprul khro mang 'khrigs pas dregs pa 'dul //
NK012(na)001:1455: ye shes thugs kyi sras la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK012(na)001:1456: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK012(na)001:1457: bdud 'dul mthu chen khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK012(na)001:1458: don dam zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK012(na)001:1459: thabs mkhas thugs rje khro bo'i skur ston pa //
NK012(na)001:1460: nyon mongs log par lta ba'i bgegs rnams 'joms //
NK012(na)001:1461: yang dag lam la gdug pa 'god mdzad pa'i //
NK012(na)001:1462: lhun gyis grub pa drag po'i phrin las rnams //
NK012(na)001:1463: mthar phyin mdzad la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK012(na)001:1464: dus gsum 'dus ma byas pa'i k+ai la ya //
NK012(na)001:1465: ma g.yos chos mchog byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK012(na)001:1466: sdug bsngal log par 'khyams pa'i sems can rnams //
NK012(na)001:1467: thugs rjes dbyer med dbyings su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK012(na)001:1468: khro rgyal 'bar ba'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:1469: lang lab kyi rtsa dum 'khrugs sdebs rdzogs so //
NK012(na)001:1471: // sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra na mo /
NK012(na)001:1472: de nas tshogs kyi mchod pa bstan pa ni //
NK012(na)001:1473: ji ltar 'byor pa'i tshogs bshams la /
NK012(na)001:1474: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li h'u /
NK012(na)001:1479: lha gsal 'phro 'du h'u bzhi'i tshogs las bskyed //
NK012(na)001:1480: dbyings nas khro mo mngon byung hi hi bzhad //
NK012(na)001:1481: ye shes 'dus ma byas pa'i k+ai la ya //
NK012(na)001:1482: spyi bor rgya mdud bstan pa khro rgyal bcu //
NK012(na)001:1483: logs la gcum gzhogs bstan pa gzhal yas khang //
NK012(na)001:1484: sked par rgya mdud bstan pa khra thabs bcu //
NK012(na)001:1485: rtse mo zur gsum bstan pa sku gsung thugs //
NK012(na)001:1486: khong stong byang chub sems kyi thig le las //
NK012(na)001:1487: ma btab dbyings su ye nas lhun gyis grub //
NK012(na)001:1488: khro mchog 'bar ba'i sku mnga' bas //
NK012(na)001:1489: gdug pa'i gzugs can ma lus kun //
NK012(na)001:1490: lus ngag yid gsum rdul du bshig nas kyang //
NK012(na)001:1491: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK012(na)001:1492: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana ba h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1495: dam can gyi sngags brjod pas /
NK012(na)001:1500: spros pa med pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK012(na)001:1501: rnam par dag pa nas 'gro ba 'dul ba'i don
NK012(na)001:1502: la byon pa / sku gsung thugs kyi sprul pa //
NK012(na)001:1503: yab bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK012(na)001:1505: sras ye shes kyi khro bo pha bcu /
NK012(na)001:1509: thugs las skyes pa'i sras mchog /
NK012(na)001:1510: ye shes kyi sgo ma bzhi /
NK012(na)001:1511: dam can shwa na ma mched bzhi /
NK012(na)001:1521: 'khor tshogs rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1522: hoh gzhan yang rnal 'byor pa bdag gi tshogs kyi
NK012(na)001:1523: mchod pa nam mkha'i rgyan skar tshogs ltar bkram pa
NK012(na)001:1524: / sa gzhi'i rgyan rtsi shing dang nags tshal ltar gtibs pa /
NK012(na)001:1525: bar snang gi rgyan sprin dang 'ja' tshon ltar spungs pa /
NK012(na)001:1530: reg bya la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon tan dpag tu med pa 'bul zhing mchis na /
NK012(na)001:1531: dgyes pa chen pos longs spyod par ci gnang //
NK012(na)001:1534: mthing nag 'bar ba'i pho brang du //
NK012(na)001:1536: sgrib pa rnam gnyis sbyangs pa dang //
NK012(na)001:1537: tshogs gnyis rdzogs par bgyi slad du //
NK012(na)001:1538: 'byor tshogs gzhung dang mthun par 'bul lags na //
NK012(na)001:1539: thugs dam bskang ngo byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK012(na)001:1541: rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK012(na)001:1542: chos kun sgyu mar rig par bya //
NK012(na)001:1543: rig pa'i ye shes ra zhes bya //
NK012(na)001:1544: ra las ye shes me byung bas //
NK012(na)001:1545: tshogs kyi bag chags bsreg par bya //
NK012(na)001:1546: rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK012(na)001:1547: chos kun sgyu mar rig par bya //
NK012(na)001:1548: rig pa'i ye shes ya zhes bya //
NK012(na)001:1549: ya las ye shes rlung byung bas //
NK012(na)001:1550: tshogs kyi bag chags gtor bar bya //
NK012(na)001:1551: rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK012(na)001:1552: chos kun sgyu mar rig par bya //
NK012(na)001:1553: rig pa'i ye shes kha zhes bya //
NK012(na)001:1554: kha las ye shes chu byung bas //
NK012(na)001:1555: tshogs kyi bag chags bkru bar bya //
NK012(na)001:1556: thams cad ra gyis ma bsreg na //
NK012(na)001:1557: tsha ba'i dmyal ba brgyad du skye //
NK012(na)001:1558: shes rab rlung gis ma bskyod na //
NK012(na)001:1559: yang shi yang sos de las byung //
NK012(na)001:1560: dri ma chu yis ma bkrus na //
NK012(na)001:1561: grang ba'i dmyal ba brgyad du skye //
NK012(na)001:1562: sgrol ba'i gnad chen ma rtogs na //
NK012(na)001:1563: phung po bdud kyi spyod spyod yin //
NK012(na)001:1564: de phyir ra ya kha zhes bya //
NK012(na)001:1565: tshogs 'dod yon du byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK012(na)001:1566: las 'dod yon gyi lha mor byin gyis brlab /
NK012(na)001:1567: yang na snod kyi rnam pa nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor gyi nang du //
NK012(na)001:1568: tshogs kyi dngos po de tra ser por gnas pa las /
NK012(na)001:1572: 'dod yon gyi lha mo dpag tu med par bsam /
NK012(na)001:1573: mgron rnams spyan drangs pa ni /
NK012(na)001:1575: 'di na sna tshogs gzugs mchis kyis //
NK012(na)001:1576: kun kyang spyan dang gshegs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1577: 'di na sna tshogs sgra mchis kyis //
NK012(na)001:1578: kun kyang snyan dang gshegs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1579: 'di na sna tshogs dri mchis kyis //
NK012(na)001:1580: kun kyang shangs dang gshegs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1581: 'di na sna tshogs ro mchis kyis //
NK012(na)001:1582: kun kyang ljags dang gshegs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1583: 'di na sna tshogs reg mchis kyis //
NK012(na)001:1584: kun kyang sku dang gshegs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1585: 'di na sna tshogs chos mchis kyis //
NK012(na)001:1586: kun kyang thugs dang gshegs su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1587: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK012(na)001:1588: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK012(na)001:1589: lcags sgrog dga' ba'i pho nyas gnas bskyod de //
NK012(na)001:1590: rtog bral dril bus dgyes pa mchog tu bskyed //
NK012(na)001:1591: bde bshegs bzhugs shing rnam rol dgyes par mdzod //
NK012(na)001:1594: 'byung ba chen po nam mkha' che //
NK012(na)001:1596: 'dod yon mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK012(na)001:1597: gzugs ni lag gnyis me long 'dzin //
NK012(na)001:1598: gzugs mdzes bskyod pas phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK012(na)001:1599: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi mdangs ldan //
NK012(na)001:1600: gzugs kyi lha mo spyan la 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1601: sgra ni lag gnyis pi wa bsnams //
NK012(na)001:1602: bde ba'i sgra snyan phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK012(na)001:1604: dbyangs kyi lha mo snyan la 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1605: dri ni lag gnyis spos phor thogs //
NK012(na)001:1606: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa mo //
NK012(na)001:1608: kun kyang dri mchog tshim mdzad ma //
NK012(na)001:1609: dri yi lha mo shangs la 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1610: ro ni lag gnyis gzhong thogs ma //
NK012(na)001:1611: bcud ldan ro mchog lnga brgya ldan //
NK012(na)001:1612: kun kyang dri mchog tshim mdzad ma //
NK012(na)001:1613: ro yi lha mo ljags la 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1614: reg ni lag gnyis na bza' sgreng //
NK012(na)001:1615: thugs kar thim nas yongs su 'khyud //
NK012(na)001:1617: reg gi lha mo sku la 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1618: 'dod yon lha mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK012(na)001:1619: yid ni tshim par byed pas te //
NK012(na)001:1620: thams cad ma lus chos kyi dbyings //
NK012(na)001:1621: chos kyi lha mo thugs la 'bul //
NK012(na)001:1622: tshogs dgra bgegs su dmigs nas 'bul ba ni /
NK012(na)001:1623: e b+h+r+au zhes pas lcags kyi khang sgrom du bsam la /
NK012(na)001:1624: tshogs kyi dngos po dgra bgegs su bsam /
NK012(na)001:1626: phur pa yak+sha me dbal du gsal bar bskyed /
NK012(na)001:1627: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK012(na)001:1628: dzahmh'u ba hoh ka tang ka ye /
NK012(na)001:1631: a pa ra dzi te ma ra se na pra mar+d+ha na ye /
NK012(na)001:1632: dgra bgegs 'byung po sarba big+h+n+aana ba h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1633: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai li ya /
NK012(na)001:1634: dzahmh'u ba hoh ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+r+aih dan+da h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1635: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1636: sh+r+ai g+h+ram a na ya sh+r+ai g+h+ram a na ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1637: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1638: ta th+aa ya ta th+wa ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1640: dgra bgegs sarba big+h+n+aana ba h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1642: dam can rnams sha yibs la sbrang ma 'thib pa bzhin du thib thib byon par bsam /
NK012(na)001:1643: lha 'dre thams cad dbang du bsdus //
NK012(na)001:1644: snang srid thams cad zil gyis mnan par bsam zhing /
NK012(na)001:1647: bdag cag rig 'dzin sgrub pa pos //
NK012(na)001:1648: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK012(na)001:1649: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i //
NK012(na)001:1650: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK012(na)001:1651: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK012(na)001:1652: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK012(na)001:1654: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK012(na)001:1655: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK012(na)001:1656: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK012(na)001:1657: lus ngag rdul du bshig nas kyang //
NK012(na)001:1658: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK012(na)001:1659: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dgra bgegs 'byung po
NK012(na)001:1660: tri ya dzah n+ri ya dzah zhes 'gugs la bstiim
NK012(na)001:1662: sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK012(na)001:1663: rgya mdud rtse la 'brug stong ldir //
NK012(na)001:1664: steng gi lha rnams 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1665: gcum gzhogs logs la glog stong 'khyug /
NK012(na)001:1666: lha srin sde brgyad 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK012(na)001:1667: chu srin kha nas rbab ltar 'dril //
NK012(na)001:1669: rtse mo zur gsum me ltar 'bar //
NK012(na)001:1670: dbal chen rtse la me stag 'phro //
NK012(na)001:1671: bsgril ba tsam gyis srid gsum 'dar //
NK012(na)001:1672: gdengs pa tsam gyis lha rnams bsregs //
NK012(na)001:1673: btab na khams gsum thal bar rlog /
NK012(na)001:1674: bdud dang dgra bgegs smos ci dgos //
NK012(na)001:1676: phur pa de sku ri rab ltar gzi brjid che ba /
NK012(na)001:1677: de'i steng du khro bo h'u k+aa ra /
NK012(na)001:1678: de'i steng du a dkar po /
NK012(na)001:1680: badz+ra k+ai la k+ai la ya /
NK012(na)001:1686: sh+ai kri bi kri badz+ra h'u k+aa ra h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1687: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK012(na)001:1688: dzahmh'u ba hoh sarba big+h+n+aana ba h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1689: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:1694: h'u k+aa ra 'od du zhu ba las /

NK012(na)001:2025: nub phyogs pad+ma rigs kyi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:2027: dang po phud kyis mi mchod du //
NK012(na)001:2028: bcom ldan dpal chen phud kyi bdag /
NK012(na)001:2029: bar du tshogs la mi rol du //
NK012(na)001:2030: ma mo mkha' 'gro tshogs kyi bdag /
NK012(na)001:2031: tha ma lhag mas mi mchod du //
NK012(na)001:2032: ma tshogs dbang phyug lhag ma'i bdag /
NK012(na)001:2033: lhag ma kha phrus mi gdab tu //
NK012(na)001:2034: bran pho bran mo kha phru'i bdag /
NK012(na)001:2035: rnam gsum rim gyis mi mchod du //
NK012(na)001:2036: bka' dang gzhung lugs rim par yod //
NK012(na)001:2037: rnam gsum gcig tu mi bsdu rgyu //
NK012(na)001:2038: chos kyi dbyings su tha mi dad //
NK012(na)001:2039: las rnams so sor mi bcol du //
NK012(na)001:2040: las kyi gdul skal rim par yod //
NK012(na)001:2041: lta ba yangs par mi lta ru //
NK012(na)001:2042: srid gsum ye nas rnam par dag /
NK012(na)001:2043: spyod pa zhib par mi spyod du //
NK012(na)001:2044: da dung mngon par sangs ma rgyas //
NK012(na)001:2045: dkyil 'khor gra ru mi bzhag rgyu //
NK012(na)001:2046: 'byung po khyed kun mthu re chung //
NK012(na)001:2047: de la sogs te dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs //

NK012(na)001:2049: gdug pa'i tshogs 'joms mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis //
NK012(na)001:2050: zhing chen sgrol mdzad ging chen bco brgyad dang //

NK012(na)001:2057: thugs dam brda yis mtshon te gshegs su gsol //

NK012(na)001:2060: dkyil 'khor de yi phyi rim nas //

NK012(na)001:2062: phyi 'khor skyong bar zhal bzhes pa'i //

NK012(na)001:2067: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //

NK012(na)001:2070: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK012(na)001:2071: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK012(na)001:2072: rdo rje phra men rdzu 'phrul can //

NK012(na)001:2074: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK012(na)001:2075: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK012(na)001:2076: stongs khams yongs la mnga' mdzad pa'i //

NK012(na)001:2078: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //

NK012(na)001:2086: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK012(na)001:2087: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //

NK012(na)001:2094: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK012(na)001:2095: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //

NK012(na)001:2103: sring mo bzhi rnams spyan 'dren na thugs rje'i dbang gis gshegs su gsol /
NK012(na)001:2104: khyed rnams la mchod pa 'bul ba ni man chad gong gis 'gre /
NK012(na)001:2105: de nas phyi rol du brtan ma bskyang ste /
NK012(na)001:2107: dkyil 'khor de yi phyi rol na //
NK012(na)001:2108: bcom ldan dpal chen yab yum la //
NK012(na)001:2109: brtan ma'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK012(na)001:2110: bdag nyid chen mo rdo rje kun grags ma //
NK012(na)001:2111: dpal ldan ha ri rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK012(na)001:2112: sha med gangs dkar rdo rje kun tu bzang //
NK012(na)001:2113: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje g.yu ne ma //
NK012(na)001:2114: bdud mo chen mo mched bzhi yang //

NK012(na)001:2121: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK012(na)001:2122: rma ri rab mchog rdo rje grags mo rgyal //
NK012(na)001:2123: byang ri gser dang rdo rje g.yu ne ma //

NK012(na)001:2129: gtor ma longs la dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK012(na)001:2130: btsan la la ro rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK012(na)001:2131: kong btsun de mo rdo rje bod khams skyong //
NK012(na)001:2132: g.yu yi dril bu rdo rje si le ma //
NK012(na)001:2133: mo btsun ug chos rdo rje g.yar mo sil //
NK012(na)001:2134: sman mo chen mo mched bzhi yang //
NK012(na)001:2135: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor gyis bskor //
NK012(na)001:2136: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK012(na)001:2137: sil snyan mang po'i tshogs dang bcas //

NK012(na)001:2140: brtan ma chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK012(na)001:2141: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK012(na)001:2143: rlangs chen dpal gyi seng ge yi //
NK012(na)001:2144: spyan sngar khas blangs ma g.yel bar //
NK012(na)001:2145: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK012(na)001:2146: phrin las bzhi'i bro brdung ba ni /
NK012(na)001:2148: rang lhar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas /
NK012(na)001:2152: gnod byed thams cad ang+ku sha dzah gtor phor ri
NK012(na)001:2153: rab tu dmigs pa'i 'og tu gnod byed bkug la
NK012(na)001:2155: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK012(na)001:2156: shar phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK012(na)001:2157: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams la //
NK012(na)001:2158: phur pa rgya mdud rtse mo zlum //
NK012(na)001:2159: ngos la zhi ba'i lha bkod pas //
NK012(na)001:2160: btab pas thams cad zhi bar 'gyur //
NK012(na)001:2161: zhi bar ma gyur gang yang med //
NK012(na)001:2162: zhi bar mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:2164: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad kyi nad
NK012(na)001:2165: dang gdon dang bgegs dang bar chad thams cad zhi
NK012(na)001:2166: bar gyur cig sh+ain+tam ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK012(na)001:2167: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK012(na)001:2168: byang phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK012(na)001:2169: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnams la //
NK012(na)001:2170: phur pa rgya mdud rtse zur gsum //
NK012(na)001:2171: ngos la drag po'i lha bkod pas //
NK012(na)001:2172: btab pas thams cad rdul du 'gyur //
NK012(na)001:2173: rdul du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK012(na)001:2174: rdul mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:2176: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad la sdang
NK012(na)001:2177: bar byed pa'i dgra bgegs thams cad rdul du rlog
NK012(na)001:2178: cig m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK012(na)001:2179: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK012(na)001:2180: nub phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK012(na)001:2181: zangs sam dmar po'i shing rnams la //
NK012(na)001:2182: phur pa rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK012(na)001:2183: ngos la dbang gi lha bkod pas //
NK012(na)001:2184: btab pas thams cad dbang du 'gyur //
NK012(na)001:2185: dbang du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK012(na)001:2186: dbang mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)001:2188: bdag cag gis khams gsum mi nor zas gsum thams
NK012(na)001:2189: cad dbang du bsdus shig p+aa sham ku ru ye
NK012(na)001:2190: s+w+aa h+aa / stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK012(na)001:2191: lho phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK012(na)001:2192: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams la //
NK012(na)001:2193: phur pa rgya mdud rtse zur bzhi //
NK012(na)001:2194: ngos la rgyas pa'i lha bkod pas //
